OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FBy Paul Davies, Former ITV News
OL,7,FCorrespondent
OL,9,FIt was a day that would forever change
OL,10,Fthe way party conferences are held and
OL,11,Fthe security around them.
OL,13,FWe didn't know that however, as we
OL,14,Fjoined politicians and their
OL,15,Fsupporters enjoying one of the social
OL,16,Fhighlights of the political calendar.
