OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FSo that is how I came to still be up
OL,7,Fand in a bar a few doors from the
OL,8,FGrand Hotel when an IRA bomb, planted
OL,9,Fa few weeks earlier, was detonated at
OL,10,F2.54am.
OL,12,FIt was the hotel where then Prime
OL,13,FMinister Margaret Thatcher and her
OL,14,Fgovernment colleagues were staying.
OL,16,FI actually heard the blast and walked
OL,17,Fout onto the seafront to see their
OL,18,Fhotel under a cloud of dust and
OL,19,Ffalling masonry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
