OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FPersuading colleagues still in the bar
OL,7,Fthat I had witnessed an attempt to
OL,8,Fassassinate Margaret Thatcher was the
OL,9,Ffirst challenge, but I was fortunate
OL,10,Fthat the group included a cameraman,
OL,11,Fsound recordist and lighting man.
OL,13,FThe tools of their trade were locked
OL,14,Faway and there was no time to go
OL,15,Flooking for keys, so we broke into ITN
OL,16,Fcars and a secure portacabin to grab
OL,17,Fthe camera and recording equipment we
OL,18,Fwould need.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
