OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FWithin minutes of the explosion - and
OL,7,Fbefore the police had time to respond
OL,8,Fby throwing a cordon around the scene
OL,9,Fof the crime - we were in the hotel
OL,10,Fentrance seeing dust covered survivors
OL,11,Fincluding senior ministers stagger out
OL,12,Fonto the seafront.
OL,14,FMost were clearly in a state of shock.
OL,16,FWe were then able to enter the
OL,17,Fdevastated building, ITV News
OL,18,Fcameraman Nigel Thomson joining the
OL,19,Ffirst fire crews as they climbed up
OL,20,Fthrough the hotel floors searching for
OL,21,Fvictims and survivors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
