OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FThe images he captured that morning of
OL,7,Fthe devastation caused by the bomb and
OL,8,Fthe rescue of people who had been
OL,9,Fburied beneath the collapsed floors
OL,10,Fmust rate as some of the most
OL,11,Fremarkable footage filmed in Britain
OL,12,Fsince the Second World War.
OL,14,FMargaret Thatcher was applying
OL,15,Ffinishing touches to her end of
OL,16,Fconference speech when the explosion
OL,17,Fhappened. If she had been in the
OL,18,Fbathroom of her suite she may have
OL,19,Fbeen killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
