OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSubsequent investigations would
OL,12,Fdiscover that IRA bomber Patrick Magee
OL,13,Fhad checked into the Grand Hotel three
OL,14,Fand a half weeks earlier and left a
OL,15,Fbomb with a delay timer beneath the
OL,16,Fbath in a sixth floor room. Conference
OL,17,Fsecurity had been superficial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
