OL,6,FThat would never happen again, since
OL,7,F1984 the place where a party leader,
OL,8,Fespecially a Prime Minister, stays and
OL,9,Fworks during conference will be a
OL,10,Ffortress bristling with armed police
OL,11,Fand security.
OL,13,FThe Brighton bombing ended what many
OL,14,Fsee as a time of naivety and innocence.
OL,16,FYou can watch a special programme on
OL,17,Fthe Brighton Bombing - 'Bombing
OL,18,FThatcher: Brighton's night of terror'
OL,19,F- on ITVX from 4pm Thursday.
